      <body>
         <div type="edition">
            <ab>
               <lb n="1"/>
               <name type="mythical" key="Kapaneus Capne">Capne</name>
            </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>Capaneus.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Richter dates the item to the early fifth century BCE based on the artwork.
                    Athe collapsing of Capaneus, one of the seven Argive warriors fought against
                    Thebes,  is a common motif on Etruscan scrabs.</p>
         </div>
